snippet.title: Death Must Die: Act 2 - Official Reveal Trailer | Triple-I Initiative Showcase
snippet.description: Meet the Gods, see action-packed gameplay, and see what to expect with Death Must Die: Act II, available on April 20, 2024. Descend the Nether in search of Death himself! Choose from God-given powers to slay his hordes of minions. Unlock new heroes, collect powerful items and create game-breaking synergies in this roguelite hack and slash survivors game.
